OL,3,CStarmer under pressure as Burnham eyes
OL,4,Creturn to Commons
OL,6,FKeir Starmer's leadership remains
OL,7,Funder scrutiny on Friday, with
OL,8,Fpotential contenders being identified
OL,9,F- although none have yet publicly
OL,10,Fdeclared an intention to challenge him.
OL,12,FMayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,13,FBurnham confirmed on Thursday he will
OL,14,Frequest permission from Labour's
OL,15,Fruling body to stand in a by-election,
OL,16,Fpaving the way for his return to the
OL,17,FHouse of Commons.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
