FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778854269
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure as Burnham eyes
OL,4,Creturn to Commons
OL,6,FMP Josh Simons has stood down from his
OL,7,Fseat in Makerfield, where Labour holds
OL,8,Fa majority of 5,399, triggering a by-
OL,9,Felection.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FITV News understands No 10 will not
OL,17,Fseek to block Burnham from standing as
OL,18,Fa candidate, despite Labour's
OL,19,Fgoverning body preventing him from
OL,20,Fcompeting in a by-election in Gorton
OL,21,Fand Denton in February.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778854269
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure as Burnham eyes
OL,4,Creturn to Commons
OL,6,FAnnouncing his decision, Burnham said
OL,7,Fa "much bigger change was needed at a
OL,8,Fnational level", adding: "Millions are
OL,9,Fstruggling and they need the Labour
OL,10,Fgovernment to succeed."
OL,12,FBurnham's statement came on the same
OL,13,Fday Wes Streeting resigned from
OL,14,FStarmer's cabinet, telling the prime
OL,15,Fminister in a letter he had lost
OL,16,Fconfidence in his leadership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778854269
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure as Burnham eyes
OL,4,Creturn to Commons
OL,6,FReports had been mounting that the
OL,7,Fformer health secretary was planning a
OL,8,Fleadership bid, and on Wednesday, he
OL,9,Fmet with Starmer at Downing Street for
OL,10,Fa discussion which lasted just 16
OL,11,Fminutes.
OL,13,FStreeting wrote in his resignation
OL,14,Fletter: "You have many great strengths
OL,15,Fthat I admire. You led our party to a
OL,16,Fvictory few thought possible in 2024
OL,17,Fand I was proud to fight alongside you
OL,18,Fin the trenches of that campaign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778854269
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure as Burnham eyes
OL,4,Creturn to Commons
OL,6,F"You have shown courage and
OL,7,Fstatesmanship on the world stage ` not
OL,8,Fleast in keeping Britain out of the
OL,9,Fwar in Iran.
OL,11,F"But where we need vision, we have a
OL,12,Fvacuum. Where we need direction, we
OL,13,Fhave drift."
OL,15,FStarmer responded to Streeting with a
OL,16,Fletter, praising his work in
OL,17,Fgovernment and stating that he had "no
OL,18,Fdoubt you will continue to play an
OL,19,Fimportant role in our party for many
OL,20,Fyears to come".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778854269
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure as Burnham eyes
OL,4,Creturn to Commons
OL,6,F"Everyone in our party is acutely
OL,7,Faware that our opponents are more
OL,8,Fdangerous than ever before," Starmer
OL,9,Fwrote.
OL,11,F"They are a real threat to the values
OL,12,Fwe care about, to the communities we
OL,13,Frepresent and to the country we love.
OL,14,FIt is incumbent on all of us to rise
OL,15,Fto what I see as a battle for the soul
OL,16,Fof our nation."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778854269
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure as Burnham eyes
OL,4,Creturn to Commons
OL,6,FStreeting's resignation does not
OL,7,Fimmediately trigger a leadership
OL,8,Fcontest, with any MP wishing to do so
OL,9,Fneeding the public backing of 81
OL,10,FLabour MPs.
OL,12,FAllies of the former health secretary
OL,13,Finsist Streeting has these numbers,
OL,14,Fbut until a contest is officially
OL,15,Flaunched, it is unclear exactly how
OL,16,Fmuch support Streeting carries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778854269
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure as Burnham eyes
OL,4,Creturn to Commons
OL,6,FAnother name in the mix is Angela
OL,7,FRayner, the former deputy prime
OL,8,Fminister who was forced to step down
OL,9,Flast year after she was found to have
OL,10,Fbroken ministerial code by underpaying
OL,11,Fstamp duty on an #800,000 flat she
OL,12,Fconsidered her second home.
OL,14,FAngela Rayner spoke exclusively to ITV
OL,15,FNews after being cleared by HMRC in
OL,16,Fher ongoing tax dispute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778854269
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure as Burnham eyes
OL,4,Creturn to Commons
OL,6,FRayner told ITV News an HMRC
OL,7,Finvestigation had cleared her of any
OL,8,Fwrongdoing, after concluding she had
OL,9,Fnot sought to avoid paying the correct
OL,10,Fstamp duty on the purchase of her
OL,11,Fproperty in 2025.
OL,13,F"I'd taken advice and felt I'd done
OL,14,Fthe right thing and it was right for
OL,15,Fme to stand down from government and
OL,16,Fto comply with HMRC, which is what
OL,17,FI've done," Rayner said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778854269
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure as Burnham eyes
OL,4,Creturn to Commons
OL,6,FRayner did not rule out making a bid
OL,7,Ffor No 10, but said she "would not
OL,8,Ftrigger the prime minister" and also
OL,9,Fdenied that she had made a leadership
OL,10,Fpact with Burnham.
OL,12,FBackers of Andy Burnham favour a
OL,13,Flonger leadership contest, which would
OL,14,Fgive him the time to become an MP and
OL,15,Fthrow his own name into the ring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778854269
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure as Burnham eyes
OL,4,Creturn to Commons
OL,6,FAn earlier contest benefits
OL,7,FStreeting's own chances, but
OL,8,Fregardless of who stands, Starmer has
OL,9,Finsisted he will fight them, with at
OL,10,Fleast 100 MPs signing a letter
OL,11,Fsupporting him, though several have
OL,12,Fsince claimed their names were added
OL,13,Fwithout their consent.
OL,15,FResponding to Streeting's departure,
OL,16,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,17,Fsaid it was a chance for Labour to
OL,18,F"draw a line" under the leadership
OL,19,Fdebate.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
